title: Ten Hag's Overconfidence?
description:
The FC crew continue to react to the fallout from Manchester City's dominant derby display and question if Erik ten Hag went into the match with too much confidence in himself. Plus, Julien Laurens joins the show to provide an update on Christopher Nkunku's possible move to Chelsea and celebrate Zlatan Ibrahimovic's 41st birthday.
